1. *Nekim* ljudima je lakše da se nose sa gubitkom nego sa uspehom. (Some people find it easier to cope with loss than with success.)

2. On je *nekim* čudnim činom postao izuzetno bogat. (He became extremely rich by some strange act.)

3. *Nekim* srećnim slučajem uspeli smo da izbegnemo sudbinu koja je čekala druge. (By some lucky chance, we managed to avoid the destiny that awaited others.)

4. Ono što se dešavalo je bilo nekim čudom. (What was happening was a sort of a miracle.)

5. *Nekim* ljudima je potrebna pomoć da bi se snašli u životu. (Some people need help to find their way in life.)